refactoring.comment: Extract Track in FooBarCamp.conference: - specific for the generic refactoring 'ExtractXwithReferenceClass' - executable for the language CONFERENCE (http://www.emftext.org/language/conference) - refactored elements: - has the following generic description: This role model describes all roles being used to express the original Martin Fowler refactoring Extract Method. Therein statements contained in a method (e.g. Java) will be selected and removed to a newly created method. At the old position of the statements a method call will be set instead.
